  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time solar/load/grid balance monitoring with 10-second updates",
    "Automatic load control with up to 3 configurable devices and priority logic",
    "Persistent alerts for sustained export and import conditions",
    "Multiple optimization strategies (maximize self-consumption, avoid grid import, balanced)",
    "Built-in simulation mode with 3 profiles for testing without hardware",
    "Anti-flapping protections with configurable min_on_time and cooldown periods",
    "UI-based configuration through Home Assistant (no YAML required)",
    "Importable dashboard templates for energy visualization"
  ],
